reviewText: It was a gift and although it wasn't the exact item he wanted, he liked this better.

Although I read the initial rather poor reviews on this and dismissed it, I recently read another review that changed my mind. While it wasn't raving, it was a rather positive review. I ordered it and was riveted to the story. There is a lot of the familiar footage, but it's rather skillfully integrated into a program that actually offers new information and a "long view" of what the title says - The Who, Mods and and Quadrophenia. I will enjoy this program for years.
